column2: City Break to a European City
column10:
Explore some of the best European cities in the world and enjoy a three night trip including flights, hotel and return transfers to any of the following major cities: Barcelona, Madrid, Amsterdam, Palma or Rome
Reward includes:
  • Package for 2 people
  • Three night's accommodation in a 4* Hotel including breakfast
  • Return flights
  • Return airport transfers (in chosen destination)

Treat the family to a three night breakaway in an Executive Lodge to a Center Parcs location of your choice. Choose from up to 200 indoor and outdoor activities, make a splash in the world-famous Subtropical Swimming Paradise, and dine in a range of restaurants.
Reward includes:
  • Package for 4 people (2 adults and 2 children)
  • 3 Nights Accommodation in the Standard Executive Lodge. Some advantages include luxury bed linen, flatscreen TVs, WiFi and daily maid service
  • Choice of locations include: Whinfell Forest (Cumbria) Sherwood Forest (Nottingham) Elvedon Forest (Suffolk) Woburn Forest (Bedfordshire) Longleat Forest (Wiltshire)

Explore the capital city of London and enjoy an overnight stay in a 4* Hotel including breakfast. Enjoy an early evening meal taking in a West End show of your choice.
Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • 4* Hotel accommodation including breakfast for one night
  • Evening Meal allocation
  • West End Show Tickets

column2: London Weekend Stay including Thames Dinner Cruise on the Bateaux London
column10:
Enjoy the capital city of London including overnight accommodation in a 4* central Hotel and a prestigious dinner cruise on the famous Bateaux London. Complementing the spectacular sights of London is the evening's entertainment performed by the resident band, compromising some of London's finest musicians.
Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • 4* Hotel accommodation including breakfast for one night
  • 3 Course Bateaux Dinner Cruise including Welcome drink, Four Course a la carte menu with house wine and mineral water, tea and coffee, Live Band

column2: A trip on the Belmond British Pullman Golden Age of Travel
column10:
Step back into the glamorous 1920s aboard the Belmond British Pullman. Dress to impress and experience true vintage luxury, highlighted by tantalising modern cuisine. Gleaming carriages pull into the station and your glamorous host invites you to board. Enjoy fine food and wine as you set off on a round-trip through Britain's glorious countryside.
Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • Round-trip aboard the train departing from London Victoria
  • Five-course lunch with Laurent-Perrier champagne
  • Half a bottle of wine per person

See the beautiful city of Dublin with this trip to Ireland for two people to include return flights from your chosen airport, overnight accommodation including breakfast at the 4* Doubletree Hilton Hotel along with an evening meal at a restaurant in Dublin.
Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • Return Flights from preferred airport
  • 4* Hotel accommodation at Doubletree Hilton Hotel including breakfast for one night
  • Evening Meal allocation at restaurant

column2: Champagne, Canapes & Cruise down the River Thames
column10:
Relax and enjoy an exclusive Champagne & Canape cruise down the river Thames from the picturesque and historic town of Henley on Thames on a Date to be confirmed.

You and three guests will board the luxurious "Hibernia" at the home of the world famous Henley Royal Regatta, and embark upon a relaxed and leisurely one and a half hour cruise, taking in the changing panorama and spectacular views of the river from the splendour of this beautifully glass encased luxury vessel. Your cruise will include unlimited complimentary champagne and canapes for you and your guests throughout the duration of your journey. Reward includes:
  • Four People
  • Complimentary Champagne and Canapes
  • Duration around 1Hr 30Mins

column2: VIP Family Fun Day at Theme Park
column10:
Enjoy a VIP Experience at Alton Towers or Thorpe Park Theme Park for 4 people (2 adults & 2 children) Reward includes:
  • Theme Park Entry
  • Meal Deals
  • Car Parking
  • Fastrack Adventurer *Depending on Theme Park Selected.

Live music, sport, comedy and family entertainment. Enjoy a day a superb hospitality event for 2 people at the Genting Arena. Choose a music, sport, comedy or family entertainment event at one of the very best venues in the UK. Various dates and events available. Date selection confirmed upon completion of promotion. Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • Hospitality Package at Genting Arena (various options available)

Satisfy your need for speed with four spectacular supercars! You won’t be disappointed as you glide round the track in these infamous high–performance cars. Ever wanted to drive a Ferrari, Lamborghini, Nissan GTR and an Aston Martin on the same day.
Reward includes:
  • Two people
  • Drive Four Cars – From either a Ferrari, Lamborghini, Nissan GTR, Aston Martin, Audi R8 and a Porsche.
  • Drive in the locations: Prestwold Driving Centre (Leicestershire), Elvington (Yorkshire), Dunsfold (Surrey), Sherburn in Elmet (Leeds), Stratford upon Avon (Warwickshire) and Lydden Hill (Kent)
  • Selected dates from March-November.

column2: Hospitality Day at the Races – Various Racecourses
column10:
Enjoy a day at the races with a superb hospitality day for 2 people. Enjoy the beautiful settings and fantastic facilities the racecourses have to offer and see if you can pick a winner! *Various dates available. Date selection confirmed upon completion of promotion Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • Hospitality Day at various racecourses (subject to availability)
  • Locations include: Cheltenham, Newbury, Ascot, Haydock, Chester, Aintree, York, Sandown & Bath

One night accommodation for 2 people at your choice of Hotel du Vin collection including breakfast and evening meal. Locations include: Bristol, Birmingham, Henley, Winchester, Poole, Cheltenham, Newcastle, Brighton, Tunbridge Wells, Harrogate, York, Cambridge, Glasgow and Edinburgh. Reward includes:
  • Package for two people
  • Accommodation at selected Hotel du Vin for one night.
  • Evening Meal allocation at Hotel restaurant

column2: Exclusive Golf Package at Celtic Manor Resort
column10:
Taylor Made Club Fitting Package at exclusive Celtic Manor Hotel - Reward for 4 people. Lead person (1) will be kitted out with a TaylorMade stand-bag and custom-fitted M2 irons (4-9 + PW, SW or AW) which will be fitted to their swing. Enjoy 18 holes of golf on either of the Championship Roman Road or Montgomerie courses, hosting some of the best holes in world golf. This reward also includes overnight accommodation in two Superior Rooms including breakfast.
Reward includes:
  • Round of 18 holes for 4 people at the Celtic Manor
  • The Lead Person will have custom fitted M2 Irons which are fitted to their swing
  • Overnight Accommodation including breakfast and Two superior twin rooms

The neon lights of the Las Vegas strip are a must see. With the extravagant hotels, casinos and amazing restaurants there is so much to do and enjoy in Las Vegas. This reward is for 2 people and includes return flights and airport transfers including accommodation for 3 nights in a 4* Las Vegas Hotel.
Package Includes:
  • Package for 2 people
  • Three night's accommodation in a 4* Hotel.
  • Return flights
  • Return airport transfers

Whether you're looking for a relaxing beach holiday or to explore the many corners of the city, Dubai offers the best of both worlds. Enjoy the sun and sand in one of the many luxury resorts, take in the breath-taking views from atop the world's tallest skyscraper, and visit the waterfront galleries and cafes in the old Bastakia Quarter. This reward is for 2 people and includes return flights and airport transfers including accommodation for 3 nights in a 4* Hotel.
Package Includes:
  • Package for 2 people
  • Three nights accommodation in a 4* Hotel including Breakfast
  • Return flights
  • Return airport transfers

Enjoy the sights and sounds of New York City as you stroll through iconic Central Park, take a trip out to Ellis Island and stumble upon some of the many outdoor art fairs, markets and events that fill the city streets. This reward is for 2 people and includes return flights and airport transfers including accommodation for 3 nights in a 4* Hotel.
Package Includes:
  • Package for 2 people
  • Three night's accommodation in a 4* Hotel
  • Return flights
  • Return airport transfers

One of the most fascinating and astonishing places in the world, enjoy a 3 night trip to the Ice Hotel in Sweden to include return flights and transfers, accommodation at the Ice Hotel to include 1 night in an Art Suite (cold room). The reward also includes a Northern Lights Snowmobiling Tour including dinner at a wilderness hut.
Package includes:
  • Package for 2 people
  • Three night's accommodation including Breakfast
  • Return flights
  • Return airport transfers
  • Northern Lights snowmobile tour

The Algarve is an ideal destination for holidays in Portugal. Perched on a red clifftop in the south of the country, Da Balaia Club Med looks out over the Atlantic Ocean.
  • Only a 20 minute transfer from the airport
  • Enjoy elegant comfort and fine food with delicious, creative cuisine and impeccable table art. The chefs really let their creative juices flow to ensure you have a fabulous and entertaining meal.
  • Relax at Club Med Spa by CINQ MONDES
  • Leave your children in the capable hands of our G.O’s, from 4 months old
  • Enjoy the wonderful nature and culture of the Algarve
  • Perfect your swing at the Golf School or on one of the Algarve's prestigious courses
  • Experience the thrill of the new flying trapeze
  • Club Med Da Balaia Accommodation
  • Flights from Birmingham or Gatwick to Faro
  • 1st – 8th June 2017
  • All Inclusive Package for food and beverage
* This incentive is separate to the other promotions being offered and requires a financial commitment upon sign up. The target period is run the same way, however there is a travel fee of £425 and a £2,000 (plus vat) charge which is reimbursed once the target has been achieved (with a sliding scale of credits to 50% of target achieved).
